      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h2>
      
      <p>By using <strong>InstaSnapper.com</strong>, you agree to follow all the privacy policies outlined on this page. InstaSnapper is a simple tool created to help users download public Instagram Reels and YouTube Shorts — nothing more, nothing less.</p>
      
