      <p>🧠 Some ads on InstaSnapper may be delivered by third-party networks, advertising agencies, or audience providers. These third parties may use cookies, web beacons, and similar technologies to understand your online behavior and serve relevant ads. We are not responsible for how they use your information and recommend reviewing their privacy policies.</p>
      
      <p>🔒 We do not sell, trade, or transfer your personal information to outside parties — because we don’t collect it in the first place. However, we may use third-party services to operate the website, and they are required to keep any technical data confidential.</p>
      
      <p>📌 Occasionally, we may link to third-party tools or services that may have their own privacy policies. We are not responsible for the content or practices of these external sites but welcome any feedback if you face issues with them.</p>
      
      <p>📅 Any future changes to our Privacy Policy will be updated right here on this page. We encourage users to check back occasionally to stay informed.</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for trusting <strong>InstaSnapper</strong> — your go-to tool for fast, secure, and simple Instagram Reels and YouTube Shorts downloading. 🚀</p>
